graph TD
    Q[(Goal Queue<br/>Cosmos DB)] --> P[Pick Next Goal]
    P --> L[Load Goal State<br/>+ Current Plan]
    L --> I[Run One Iteration<br/>Single LLM Call]
    I --> S{Goal Complete?}

    S -->|No| U[Update Plan<br/>in Database]
    U --> Q

    S -->|Yes| C[Mark Completed]
    S -->|Failed| F[Mark Failed<br/>+ Record Error]
    S -->|Over Budget| B[Pause + Re-queue]

    style Q fill:#4a9eff,color:#fff
    style I fill:#ff9f43,color:#fff
    style C fill:#2ecc71,color:#fff
    style F fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff
